{"tid":1864511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】4名確診者求診私家醫生名單曝光","createTime":"2020-02-05T15:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T16:01:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad68c7c17cffc3bccb502ae1950e87f87be7c78","tid":1864511,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"疫情肆虐，本港單日再增至少3宗武漢肺炎確診個案，特首林鄭月娥都在記者會上亦首度承認，可能已經出現社區傳染。全民關注確診患者此前曾到過甚麼地方，《蘋果》整合了資料供讀者參考。日前確診的第16宗個案、64歲恆豐中心時裝店店主，她曾向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>趙崇就醫生（佐敦彌敦道301-309號嘉賓商業大廈4902室）</strong></span>求診，求診日期有待確認，也於1月31日向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>盧柏參醫生求診（九龍馬頭圍道350號地下）</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n至於早前藍田一家三口都證實確診，居於藍田康田苑的60歲男病人，就先後四次到私家診所求醫。最早於1月23日向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">邱榕生醫生（九龍藍田匯景商場5樓48舖）</span></strong>求診，其後於1月26日向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九龍灣德福花園I座地下卓健醫療中心的Jason Wan醫生</span></strong>求診，又於1月29日向同一診所的陳健靈醫生求診，最後於1月31日向同一診所的張文基醫生診。其28歲女兒於1月31日向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>蔡志強醫生（藍田匯景道1-17號匯景廣場5樓40A-41室）</strong></span>求診，及於2月3日向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>聯保醫務所（尖沙嘴亞士厘道9-11號順豐大廈14樓）</strong></span>求診。<br />\n<br />\n最新一宗56歲男病人個案，曾於2月2日向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鍾天德醫生（沙田新城市商業大廈9樓卓健醫療體檢中心）</strong></span>求診。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，衞生署會向有關私家醫生了解當時求診情況，如醫生有否戴口罩，或與病人接觸時間多久等，決定醫生是否密切接觸者、是否需入隔離營。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/XFEIIFBLIXFUKCQSN4BJGTGEFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FXFEIIFBLIXFUKCQSN4BJGTGEFQ%2F&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=50ef17fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FXFEIIFBLIXFUKCQSN4BJGTGEFQ%2F&h=a9e5dba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/XFEIIFBLIXFUKCQSN4BJGTGEFQ/</a>"},{"pid":"43d4258a0fcfecda0cdbb88f90321f30cd62f559","tid":1864511,"uid":128271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"卓健連中兩元<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022d37b825f9bf4668bf6b46b7cc95b930162481","tid":1864511,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"佐敦彌敦道301-309號嘉賓商業大廈4902室<br />\n九龍馬頭圍道350號地下<br />\n九龍藍田匯景商場5樓48舖<br />\n九龍灣德福花園I座地下卓健醫療中心<br />\n藍田匯景道1-17號匯景廣場5樓40A-41室<br />\n尖沙嘴亞士厘道9-11號順豐大廈14樓<br />\n沙田新城市商業大廈9樓卓健醫療體檢中心"},{"pid":"53ac0bc8963df6ddbf0fd351315b982ef0a9a55c","tid":1864511,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d4258a0fcfecda0cdbb88f90321f30cd62f559","tid":1864511,"uid":128271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"卓健連中兩元<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"佢連去三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d126595105d85dc8ae4a7fdca4569a22b4ae90","tid":1864511,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa57bc77712b43492feb88d1eff8dd0535cb962","tid":1864511,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"岀街帶多幾個口罩比有需要嘅人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1864513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1864513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ba908fab02c6c0d80c32be455f7bbae75aa27035","tid":1864511,"uid":237300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"嘉賓成幢都係診所，呢排無咩特別事真係少去為妙"},{"pid":"88f16fbce52b313d9710fdb843175d36c0e2d7d1","tid":1864511,"uid":24227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"生意仆直 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}